  abstract   = {Neural controllers are able to position the hand-held
                camera of the (3DOF) anthropomorphic OSCAR-robot manipulator above an
                object which is arbitrary placed on a table. The desired camera-joint
                mapping is approximated by feedforward neural networks. However, if the
